Title: Assess system responses to the questions

Input.questions: ['What is the role of Co-Extra in GMO food traceability in the EU?', 'Why did the Airbus A380 stop being produced?', 'What are the other natural wonders of the world besides the Great Barrier Reef?', 'How often should I run to lose weight?', 'What’s the best bike seat', 'Tell me about the different types of rocket engines.', 'Interesting. What was the basis of the backlash Marvel Studios faced for the Vice President’s suggestion that diversity was causing sales to slide?', 'How do you get impartial results from search engines?', 'What licenses and permits are needed for a food truck?', 'I like hiking and Malbec wine. You mentioned some high peaks. How can I hike some high mountains and visit some wineries famous for Malbec?']
Input.answers: ['Co-Extra, an EU-funded research program, primarily focused on developing genetically modified organisms (GMOs) that could be used to enhance food traceability in the European Union. Their goal was to create GMOs with unique genetic markers that could be easily detected in food products. By introducing these GMOs into the supply chain, Co-Extra aimed to establish a foolproof traceability system, ensuring consumers could track the origin of their food accurately.', 'The Airbus A380 ceased production primarily due to a combination of factors, including declining demand for such large aircraft, high production costs, and a shift in the airline industry toward point-to-point systems. Airbus announced the discontinuation in February 2019 after its main customer, Emirates, reduced its A380 order and shifted to smaller, more fuel-efficient aircraft like the A330-900 and A350-900. With production costs exceeding the selling price and airlines favoring point-to-point routes over hub-and-spoke systems, the A380 program became economically unsustainable for Airbus, leading to the decision to stop production.', "The other Natural Wonders of the World besides the Great Barrier Reef include the Grand Canyon, Northern Lights, Mt. Everest, Dead Sea, Victoria Falls, and Kilimanjaro. These wonders are remarkable geological features and natural phenomena created by the forces of nature over time, showcasing the Earth's diverse and awe-inspiring landscapes and events.", "To lose weight through running, it's essential to combine your running program with a balanced diet. Danish research shows that new runners seeking weight loss who ran more than 5km (3.1 miles) per week for one year and adjusted their diets lost an average of 12.3 pounds, while those who didn't change their diets lost 8.4 pounds. For faster weight loss, consider gradually increasing your running duration and frequency (with a long-term goal of building up to 60 minutes of running per day, six days per week), but remember that a well-balanced diet remains crucial to achieving your goals.", 'Highly recommended bike seat is the Brooks England Cambium C-17 Saddle. It offers maintenance-free use, waterproof properties, and exceptional comfort for long rides. Its design, including flexibility on rough terrain and suitability for touring enthusiasts and bike packers, makes it a top choice for comfortable and versatile cycling experiences.', 'Rocket engines can be categorized into four main types based on their propulsion methods. Solid-fuel rockets use propellant in a solid phase, while liquid-propellant rockets rely on propellants in a liquid state fed from tanks. Hybrid rockets combine a solid propellant with a liquid or gas oxidizer, and monopropellant rockets use a single propellant decomposed by a catalyst. These different types of engines have diverse applications and performance characteristics in rocketry.', "The backlash faced by Marvel Studios for the Vice President's suggestion that diversity was causing sales to decline centered around the perception that Marvel was facing criticism for altering existing characters to be more diverse rather than creating entirely new characters or reintroducing old ones that better reflected various communities. David Gabriel's remarks at the Marvel Retailer Summit, where he mentioned a reluctance toward diversity among readers, sparked controversy. This incident highlighted Hollywood's ongoing diversity issues, particularly in big-budget superhero movies.", 'To obtain impartial search engine results, ensure you clear your browser cookies and history regularly, use a variety of search engines, and search in incognito mode to avoid personalization. This will help eliminate bias and provide a more neutral search experience. Additionally, it is useful to search using specific keywords provided by the search engine companies themselves, as this ensures unbiased and neutral information retrieval.', "The licenses and permits needed for a food truck vary by country and locality. In Toronto, Canada, requirements include business and liability insurance, a Commercial Vehicle Operator's Registration for the truck, permits for each municipality it operates in, a food handler certificate, the appropriate driver's licenses, assistant's licenses for assistants, and a health inspection, among others.", 'To combine hiking and Malbec wine, plan a trip to the Penedès region in Catalonia. You can explore the Montserrat mountain range, which offers fantastic hiking opportunities, and then visit renowned wineries in the Penedès, known for its exceptional Malbec wine production. This region offers a perfect blend of outdoor adventure and wine tasting experiences.']
